          difference in the communities they are in. These schools bring
          education to faraway places, helping the communities grow and improve.
          By giving people access to education, we help them become stronger and
          create a culture where learning is important.
          <br /><br />Our focus on education in remote areas helps people break
          free from poverty. Education gives them a chance to learn important
